-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Safety defaults
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The server starts in TM1_MODE=readonly. Write and destructive tools (delete,
upsert, import, save-data, run-process, etc.) are NOT registered unless you
explicitly set TM1_MODE=readwrite. Do not run a readwrite server against a
production instance without reviewing the write path first.

